-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project Description
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository contains third-party plugins for the MysticThumbs Windows
thumbnail provider. These plugins extend MysticThumbs with additional
thumbnail generation capabilities, including but not limited to:

- SVG thumbnails using the resvg rendering library
- Video and media thumbnails using FFmpeg
- DLL inspection thumbnails and other experimental generators

The code in this repository is an independent project developed by
Voith's CODE.


