-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FFmpeg Notice
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The FFmpeg-based plugin dynamically links against FFmpeg libraries.
Users are free to replace the FFmpeg DLLs distributed with the plugin
with their own builds of FFmpeg if desired, subject to the licensing
terms of FFmpeg.


